Game Notes
~~~~~~~~~~
THE OLD WEST, 1864. In order to save their family, the McCall brothers will
kill anyone who stands between them and the legendary Gold of Juarez.
But when the allure of women and money tests their bond as brothers, will
the blood they share prove to be thicker?
